profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

profile:
We are Ontario’s premier home renovation company. Our experts are passionate about building you the home of your dreams. With over 12 years of industry experience in basement renovations, bathroom renovations, and home-building solutions, we have satisfied hundreds of homeowners. And we’d love to do the same for you for your home renovation.

For all your home renovation needs–whether a bathroom makeover or a basement renovation or Kitchen remodelling, whatever your intentions – we have the know-how to see the job through to success. 

Our team brings the ideas, creativity, and know-how that will make a real difference in your home renovation project, saving you money and finding the perfect combination of style and function.

Founded on basic tenets like fairness and trust, Domilya Group works with you to transform renovation ideas into top-quality results that will leave you with the space you have envisioned. 

Home renovation projects can be stressful, but we take the extra steps to make it hassle-free for you. This becomes possible because of our unique approach, which we feel sets us apart.


Need something installed?  We install it all. All work is done right the first time because we take great pride in our work. 


Redo Your Home Right:

If you need a bathroom, basement, a kitchen or whole home renovations, we provide the materials and know-how.

We know what it takes to protect your home and make it look beautiful. We guarantee all of our work. 


We provide top-notch construction at competitive pricing.

Most of our services are provided to homeowners who want to modernize their residences, such as updating or enlarging an existing kitchen or bathroom, finishing a basement or a complete gut job. We specialize in helping prepare homes for sale and being on time and on budget.   


Home Improvement time is here!
Fast, Friendly, Professional Service with Quality Workmanship. 
Our team will work hard for you to make your renovation dream come true.


We offer:

*Preparing Homes for Sale
*Finishing Basements
*Bathroom & Kitchen Renovations
*Flooring–(Laminate, Hardwood, Carpet and Ceramic, Marble)
*Framing & Taping
*Painting
*Home Remodeling
*Home Renovations
*Electrical & Plumbing (subcontracted to licensed trades-persons)
And much more!


We are geared to delivering specialized home remodeling services to clientele in the Greater Toronto Area, Halton, and Peel Region. Our quality approach and efforts ensure that your renovating project is designed and completed just the way you imagined it.


Let us refurbish your home from top to bottom. 

Here are some examples of the work we do- 
Doors,  Windows, Painting, Backsplash, Kitchen Renovations, Bathroom Renovations, Interior Work, Finishing Basements, Tiles, Faucets & Sinks, Custom Design, Extensions, Drywall, Shower Doors, Drywall Framing, Closet Doors, Shower Enclosures,  Crown Mouldings, General Carpentry, Flooring, Interior Finishing, Floor Leveling, Hardwood, Laminate, Small Renovations, Bathroom Remodeling, Kitchen  Remodeling, Cabinet Installations, Interior Painting, Bathroom Vanities, Laminate Installation, Hardwood Installation, Tub Enclosures, Ceramic, Wall Plastering, Ceiling Painting & Repair, Finishing Basements, Changing Stairs.

profile:
LONI Aluminum & Contracting has established itself as one of Ontario’s leading Siding, Soffit & Fascia, Windows and Doors installation, and replacement companies. We have serviced homeowners for over 20 years and we continue to provide innovative home improvement products that exceed industry standards for quality, reliability, and performance.
 
 We use highly specialized installation techniques to ensure a lifetime of satisfaction from our customers. We always strive to go beyond our customer’s requirements for beautiful, strong and thermally efficient products.
 
Quality, commitment, and the promise of product longevity are the core philosophies of LONI Aluminum & Contracting. All of our installations are warranted for life, if any sort of failure does occur we will fix or replace the defect, free of charge for as long as you own the home.
 
We carry a $2,000,000 Liability insurance to make sure safety is our top priority. All of our workers are covered by WSIB workers compensation. If we get hurt on your property, you’re not liable in any way. Copies supplied upon request.
 
When you call LONI Aluminum & Contracting, you will be greeted with a courteous, knowledgeable staff member who will be happy to assist you in any capacity. If an appointment is set we will email you a confirmation with the time and date. One of our very experienced representatives will arrive ON TIME and give you a no pressure demonstration specific to the product your interested in. They’ll then leave you with a price which is good for 30 days.
 
LONI Aluminum & Contracting covers the entire Greater Toronto area and some parts of Northern and Southern Ontario. If you decide to move forward with us, we’ll write a detailed agreement including all the specifications we discussed. Most projects are completed within 3 to 4 weeks of the agreement. We won’t accept final payment until you are 100% satisfied.
 
Call us at 905-463-1803 for a free quote today! For out of office hours, we can be reached at 647-833-7665 (call or text).
 
 
Check us out on Instagram! https://www.instagram.com/lonialuminum/

profile:
The home is - for most of us - the single most important investment and asset that we will own in our lifetimes.  Period.
It's where we live, where we raise our families, and it's where we build our wealth.  At McLaren Custom Homes we understand this.  Your home and -  more importantly - your plans for it, are important to us.  But let's face it, re-models can be overwhelming!!  Its hard to know where to start, who to talk to, who to trust!  Let us help make things EASY for you.  McLaren Custom Homes main goal is to make the whole renovation process an enjoyable experience.  We treat your home and project as if it were our own, because if it was our home we would want the best.   

  Our diverse team specializes in the following:
- Project Design
- Building Permit Application Packages
- New Building and Additions
- Full or Partial Renovations
- Kitchen Re-models
- Exterior Spaces
- General contracting

All of us at McLaren Custom Homes strive to deliver high-quality, cost-effective projects on schedule by employing and supporting motivated, flexible, and focused teams. We are able to orchestrate your project from start to finish using our extended crew of trustworthy and professional trades while staying on time and on budget.  We value the importance of our relationships and will continue to remain fair and true in our dealings with all employees, clients, vendors, and partners. Our clients count on our dependability, our drive, and our integrity we take so much pride in our projects end results.    
 
We cannot wait to hear from you!  Please give us a call to see if McLaren Custom Homes would be good fit for your next renovation project.

At Elite Construction and Renovations, our clients needs come first. Upon your initial meeting, you’ll know you’re working with a company that cares about your project as much as you do. We promise to work with our clients to help them fulfill their vision of their dream home.
services:

ADDITIONS - Add more living space to your existing home. Our home additions are designed to give you the extra space you need to live comfortably.

RENOVATIONS - Transform your existing living space and make your dreams a reality.

UNDERPINS - Increase basement ceiling height to achieve new living space.
specialities:

It is our guarantee that if we exceed 6 months to build your custom home, we will reimburse you of any temporary living expenses you may incur.

profile:
Greenbilt was founded on the principles of creating a healthy and sustainable lifestyle for every one of our customers. There are four elements that are required in the development of a green efficient home; Energy Efficiency, Water Conservation, Waste Management, and Air Quality. It is the way we combine these four elements that presents the home owner with the best of both worlds, saving money, and saving the environment.

Green building is here, and like the evolution of the auto industry, who have seen their emissions drop and their fuel mileage increase, so will the housing industry. The 2017 Ontario Building Code is expected to increase the energy conservation requirements of new construction and we want to be one of the few to lead it into success.  We seek out the best products and techniques, and combine them into a “A la Carte” menu of green features, which then allows you to pick and choose the features you want within your green efficient home.  Greenbilt will give you insightful information and the cost-benefit analysis of your choices, so you can feel good about making informed decisions.

Here at Greenbilt, we can provide you a Green Efficient home for the same price of a conventional home. There is a vast menu of "a la carte" features that we carry for our customers to fit any need or desire they may have. If you're building a custom home, why not consider going green with Greenbilt Homes?  We have specialized in the creation of sustainable and green efficient custom homes, which is something that sets us apart from other custom home builders.  Our attention to detail and desire to inform the client about options is what ultimately produces the best home with the happiest clients. 

For any questions of inquiries, I want to encourage you to give me a call. This is my work, this is my passion.
products: We have extensive knowledge about the industry, and on green products currently on or soon to be on the market.
services: Building sustainable, and green efficient homes.  What does building sustainable and green efficient mean?  It means building with the conservation of energy and water. Using sustainable strategies of passive solar, resilient materials, waste management, and incorporating a healthy life style environment of body and soul. These ideologies are supported with the creation of a tight building envelope, which represents the keystone of building green.
specialities: We have specialized in the creation of sustainable and green efficient custom homes, which is something that sets us apart from other custom home builders.

profile:
Eaglecrest New Homes Inc. is the leading full-service design and construction company focusing on turning your dream home into a reality. We design and build quality custom homes that are uniquely and meticulously tailored to your taste. With 15+ years of experience, architectural and engineering backgrounds, and being a licensed builder & designer, we provide A to Z solutions, from Concept to Key in Hand.

Being a full-service company, Eaglecrest New Homes Inc. is proudly responsible for every detail that goes into building your dream home, from style, textures, color selection, to appliances, and more. 

At Eaglecrest New Homes Inc., our mission is to find out precisely what you want and deliver it to you within your budget. This includes complete drawings, specifications, and consultation. 

Then we'll take your dream and build it for you.

profile:
Greater Toronto Contractors are home renovation experts - specializing in client experience, home designs, home additions, construction and home improvement including kitchen renovations, bathroom renovations, basement renovations & finishing. 

We're an award winning company, featured in magazines/newspapers. We have the expertise to turn your house in a home your really want to be in - at a price you can afford!

As leading Toronto General Contractors, our mission is to give home owners the best possible value for their home, while maintaining quality. With our design-build methods, we know you'll be satisfied with the end result, BEFORE we even begin renovating. Why? Using our 3D design methods, we're able to show you an accurate representation of what you'll be getting, based on your ideas, in a 3D rendered model. From there, you can quickly and easily make revisions to make your home design perfect. 

Work with our team of Toronto home renovation and Toronto construction experts to get the renovation of your dreams - using our design-build methods, we make sure that you're satisfied.
